reviews.text: Did my lashes with Tipsy Labshes with the new UV lash in 3D. I would say this is by far the best lashes extension I did as compared to others. There were no pain or irritation to my eyes. Lashes felt light weighted and comfortable. I feel this lash should be able to last quite long.

V nice ambient with tipsy lashes , smooth service as well  !! My eyes are very small ( mono-lid ) steph was helpful in advising which style would suit my eyelids ! Obsess with my lashes , Overall will definitely come back again . !!

Did my lashes before CNY and it was a good experience! Steph was very patient in answering my queries and also advising what kind of lashes would be good for me as I was not sure since it is only my third time doing lashes. Overall, nice experience and her lashes lasted even up till now, still quite full! The glue she used is also good and does not have that pricky feeling which I had from my previous lash. Definitely recommend her service!

My first time at Steph's place doing my eyelash extensions. She is very meticulous and take time to understand her clients concern. Her lashes are customised to my eye shape which really open up my eyes even more. Really love how my eyes look like after her work and definitely I will go back to her again! Her place is really comfortable and I even fall asleep during the process. Highly recommended!
